1
00:00:00,265 --> 00:00:02,828
(Rekap sebelumnya)
Aku pernah bilang kamu harus kerja keras,
itu aku mengerti.

2
00:00:02,828 --> 00:00:03,976
Tapi, kumohon padamu

3
00:00:04,007 --> 00:00:05,653
jangan lupa juga jaga diri sendiri.

4
00:00:05,687 --> 00:00:07,268
Aku kerja keras cuma buat kebaikanmu.

5
00:00:07,355 --> 00:00:09,360
Janji ya, jangan selalu lembur lagi.

6
00:00:09,992 --> 00:00:13,108
Makan yang benar, nanti aku nggak marah lagi.

7
00:00:13,265 --> 00:00:14,595
Aku janji.

8
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:32,480
(Dua hari sebelum ulang tahun North)

9
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:46,640
=Episode Spesial Ekstra Johan dan North=

10
00:01:46,810 --> 00:01:47,990
Bagus, bagus!

11
00:01:48,050 --> 00:01:50,320
Masuk, sudah hampir selesai.

12
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,990
Ini benteng terakhirnya.

13
00:01:52,030 --> 00:01:54,900
Ya, seperti itu.

14
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:56,790
Itu dia!

15
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:58,740
Menang!

16
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:03,720
(Satu hari sebelum ulang tahun North)

17
00:02:03,990 --> 00:02:05,740
Dia lagi ngapain sekarang ya?

18
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:34,420
(Selamat ulang tahun, North)

19
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:29,110
Halo, P'Jo.

20
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,680
Baru pulang kerja?

21
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:35,030
Iya. Kamu sudah tidur?

22
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:37,020
Belum.

23
00:03:37,130 --> 00:03:39,030
Jangan-jangan kamu lagi nunggu aku?

24
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:42,740
- Ehm
- Bukannya suruh kamu tidur dulu?

25
00:03:43,210 --> 00:03:46,920
Aku cuma mau ngobrol sama kamu.

26
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,210
Kamu keras kepala banget.

27
00:03:50,810 --> 00:03:53,220
Sudah sampai rumah belum?

28
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,020
Belum, aku baru keluar dari kantor.

29
00:03:56,070 --> 00:03:57,940
Wah, baru beres kerja ya?

30
00:03:58,300 --> 00:03:59,600
Iya.

31
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:01,420
North

32
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:06,170
Selamat ulang tahun!

33
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:08,150
Iya.

34
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,560
Terima kasih.

35
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:13,240
Aku orang pertama yang ngucapin?

36
00:04:13,950 --> 00:04:15,650
Sebenarnya,

37
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,740
Barusan Ter juga nelpon.

38
00:04:19,250 --> 00:04:21,620
Tapi dia nelpon sebelum tengah malam.

39
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:23,050
Jadi itu nggak dihitung.

40
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:25,450
Tapi setelah jam 12,

41
00:04:26,770 --> 00:04:28,280
kamu yang pertama, P'Jo.

42
00:04:28,590 --> 00:04:29,980
Mau aku bantu doain harapanmu?

43
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:31,470
Nggak usah.

44
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:35,320
Kayaknya kamu nggak jago ngucapin selamat.

45
00:04:37,670 --> 00:04:40,110
Maaf ya, hari ini aku nggak bisa di sisimu.

46
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,680
Kamu sekarang aja udah nemenin aku.

47
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,950
Lewat telepon aja nemenin?

48
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:47,140
Dengar suara kamu

49
00:04:47,290 --> 00:04:48,750
aja aku sudah senang.

50
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:51,910
P'Jo,

51
00:04:52,570 --> 00:04:53,480
Iya?

52
00:04:56,060 --> 00:04:57,300
Aku kangen kamu.

53
00:04:59,410 --> 00:05:01,220
Juga, hati-hati di jalan ya.

54
00:05:01,290 --> 00:05:04,600
Meski udah malam, mobilnya sepi.

55
00:05:04,990 --> 00:05:07,110
Tetap harus hati-hati.

56
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,850
Siap.

57
00:05:09,030 --> 00:05:11,230
Eh, boleh nggak sih telepon sambil nyetir?

58
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,680
Tentu aja, nih aku telepon kamu kok.

59
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:20,000
Terus, hari ini kerja gimana?

60
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:23,030
Hmm...

61
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,830
Kurang bagus.

62
00:05:27,770 --> 00:05:29,350
Kamu gimana?

63
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:32,170
Kurang baik juga.

64
00:05:35,030 --> 00:05:36,970
Boleh cerita sama aku?

65
00:05:37,940 --> 00:05:39,350
Cerita apanya?

66
00:05:39,730 --> 00:05:42,400
Tentang kerjaan kamu hari ini.

67
00:05:42,490 --> 00:05:44,070
Oh, itu nggak penting.

68
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:50,200
Tapi aku pengen denger.

69
00:05:50,380 --> 00:05:51,650
Kumohon, P'Jo.

70
00:05:51,770 --> 00:05:54,980
Tolong dong, ceritain ke aku.

71
00:05:55,130 --> 00:05:56,170
Oke, baiklah.

72
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:59,110
Timku ada perubahan orang.

73
00:05:59,110 --> 00:06:00,710
Tapi nggak ada serah terima yang cepat.

74
00:06:00,710 --> 00:06:02,670
Jadi muncul beberapa masalah.

75
00:06:03,110 --> 00:06:04,380
Dan mereka nggak bilang ke aku.

76
00:06:04,900 --> 00:06:07,590
Akhirnya aku yang harus beresin semuanya.

77
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:11,730
Padahal hari ini ulang tahunmu,

78
00:06:12,220 --> 00:06:14,050
kenapa mau dengar soal kerjaan aku?

79
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:17,190
Nggak apa-apa kok.

80
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:19,770
Asal tentang kamu, aku suka dengar.

81
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:24,530
Tapi sekarang udah beres kan?

82
00:06:24,650 --> 00:06:27,140
Belum selesai.

83
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:30,320
Meski aku nggak ngerti kerjaan kamu,

84
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:33,150
aku bakal selalu ada buat kamu, P'Jo.

85
00:06:33,470 --> 00:06:35,450
Yuk peluk, biar bisa saling recharge.

86
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:37,660
Ayo!

87
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:42,690
Maaf, aku juga nggak bisa nemenin kamu langsung.

88
00:06:43,010 --> 00:06:44,500
Nggak apa-apa kok.

89
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:47,250
Dengar suara kamu saja aku sudah lega.

90
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:50,320
Waduh, rasanya pengen nyamperin kamu lewat sinyal HP.

91
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:50,850
Lagi manja nih?

92
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:53,560
Iya, aku lagi mau manja!

93
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:56,250
Boleh lihat kamu manja nggak?

94
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:08,110
Eh, P'Jo, kamu nakal banget!

95
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,470
Nggak buka kamera, nih?

96
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,630
Nggak.

97
00:07:10,970 --> 00:07:14,630
Kenapa sih nggak mau buka? Ayo dong, aku mau lihat muka kamu.

98
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:15,970
Please?

99
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:18,230
Please buka dulu dong.

100
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:20,910
Eh, kamu masih pakai jas ya?

101
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:23,160
Iya, tadi pagi ada rapat.

102
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:27,390
Kayaknya aku belum pernah liat kamu nggak pakai jas.

103
00:07:27,910 --> 00:07:29,120
Pakai jas itu panas banget.

104
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:32,970
Kamu masih harus kerja lagi?

105
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:35,110
Masih ada sedikit urusan.

106
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:37,540
Jadi inget waktu itu...

107
00:07:37,660 --> 00:07:39,190
Maksud kamu apa?

108
00:07:39,570 --> 00:07:41,500
Pas kita ngobrol pertama kali.

109
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,550
Kita ngobrol terus

110
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:46,630
kamu kerja terus, aku nunggu sampai ketiduran.

111
00:07:47,030 --> 00:07:48,140
Oh...

112
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:49,910
Dan...

113
00:07:50,350 --> 00:07:54,370
Sekarang aku harus diem aja? Nggak boleh ganggu ya?

114
00:07:54,530 --> 00:07:55,380
Nggak perlu.

115
00:07:55,430 --> 00:07:57,710
Loh, kenapa dulu nggak boleh ngomong?

116
00:07:57,900 --> 00:07:59,490
Soalnya dulu aku belum terbiasa sama suara kamu.

117
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,530
Sekarang udah boleh ngomong belum?

118
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:03,900
Aku nggak ngelarang kok.

119
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:08,060
Aku...

120
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,670
Ada yang mau aku tanya sama kamu, P'Jo.

121
00:08:11,030 --> 00:08:12,580
Apa tuh?

122
00:08:13,050 --> 00:08:15,080
Bisa kasih tau aku, waktu ketemu aku pertama kali,

123
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:18,430
apa perasaanmu?

124
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:22,370
Ketemu kamu pertama kali?

125
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:24,830
Pas di bar itu?

126
00:08:25,250 --> 00:08:26,430
Iya.

127
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:28,870
Jelas aku kesal banget.

128
00:08:30,820 --> 00:08:32,700
Aku ngerti kok.

129
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:35,640
Tapi nggak usah galak banget ke aku, dong.

130
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,990
Tapi kan kamu pantas dapat itu.

131
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,900
- Memang sih
- Iya

132
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:45,560
Semua yang kamu lakukan bikin aku pengen ngomelin kamu.

133
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,200
Berantem di bar,

134
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,620
Kerja diam-diam, naro diri sendiri dalam bahaya.

135
00:08:51,590 --> 00:08:53,670
Setiap hari bikin aku khawatir.

136
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:57,510
Aku emang pantes dimarahin deh.

137
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:02,910
P'Jo

138
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:05,760
Ibuku nanya ke kamu,

139
00:09:06,030 --> 00:09:09,250
Liburan nggak mau jenguk dia?

140
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:11,950
Pasti mau, tapi...

141
00:09:12,290 --> 00:09:14,090
Nunggu aku selesai kerja, ya.

142
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:17,030
Oke, kalau udah tentuin waktunya bilang aja.

143
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:19,630
Aku bakal siap buat nerima kamu.

144
00:09:22,010 --> 00:09:24,840
Oh iya, gimana ulang tahunmu?

145
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:28,560
Sama aja kayak dulu, nggak ada yang spesial.

146
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:31,060
Nggak ada pesta juga.

147
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,270
Tapi mamaku beliin aku hadiah.

148
00:09:33,370 --> 00:09:34,460
Apa tuh?

149
00:09:34,610 --> 00:09:36,380
Dia beliin aku sepasang sepatu.

150
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:39,820
Masih ada yang kamu pengen nggak? Aku belum kasih hadiah soalnya.

151
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:43,150
Kamu udah kasih aku banyak barang.

152
00:09:43,940 --> 00:09:45,620
Terus...

153
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:50,970
Aku boleh minta satu hal lagi nggak?

154
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,930
Apa tuh?

155
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:57,250
P'Jo

156
00:09:58,110 --> 00:10:01,710
Kamu mau bilang "Aku cinta kamu" ke aku nggak?

157
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:05,220
- Cuma itu?
- Eh, itu bukan "cuma" lho!

158
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:08,360
Please, bilang dong.

159
00:10:15,010 --> 00:10:17,090
Aku cinta kamu, North.

160
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:20,770
Aku juga cinta kamu, P'Jo.

161
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:27,040
Kalau aku di situ, kamu pasti nggak bisa kabur deh.

162
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,730
Hah? Maksudnya apa?

163
00:10:28,730 --> 00:10:32,890
Nggak apa-apa, aku cuma mau bilang, tolong jangan terlalu imut gitu.

164
00:10:36,430 --> 00:10:37,790
Tidur, yuk.

165
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:41,810
Tapi aku masih pengen ngobrol sama kamu.

166
00:10:42,310 --> 00:10:44,500
Tidur aja, aku tetap di sini kok.

167
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:47,970
Baiklah.

168
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:03,880
Aku ingin sama kamu terus.

169
00:11:05,070 --> 00:11:09,590
Akhir-akhir ini kamu capek banget ya.

170
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:12,370
Kamu mau aku lepas kerja buat nemenin kamu?

171
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,220
Nggak mau.

172
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:17,080
Kalau gitu jangan terlalu lucu deh.

173
00:11:17,190 --> 00:11:19,360
Nanti aku beneran lepas kerja lho.

174
00:11:20,850 --> 00:11:22,980
Aku ngantuk...

175
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:25,130
Tidur aja, aku akan tetap temani kamu.

176
00:11:25,530 --> 00:11:28,350
Nggak, aku mau nemenin kamu.

177
00:11:28,470 --> 00:11:30,490
Kamu kan masih kerja.

178
00:11:30,610 --> 00:11:34,330
- Tidur aja, aku temani kamu.
- Nggak bisa, aku nggak mau tidur!

179
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:36,590
Aku mau nemenin kamu begadang.

180
00:11:37,710 --> 00:11:39,230
Kamu keras kepala banget.

181
00:11:40,470 --> 00:11:42,420
Belajar dari kamu...

182
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:46,410
Akhir-akhir ini suka banget ngeyel ya.

183
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:29,590
Ter

184
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:32,640
Selamat jalan!

185
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:36,440
P'Hill

186
00:12:44,570 --> 00:12:46,160
(Johan)

187
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:50,240
Halo

188
00:12:50,410 --> 00:12:52,270
Kamu belum tidur ya?

189
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:55,370
Iya. Kenapa cepat banget angkatnya?

190
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:57,390
Bukannya kamu bilang ngantuk?

191
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:00,310
Baru saja tiba-tiba kebangun.

192
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:03,040
Mungkin karena terlalu kangen kamu.

193
00:13:03,610 --> 00:13:05,580
Sudah selesai kerjaan?

194
00:13:05,710 --> 00:13:07,850
- Sudah selesai.
- Serius?

195
00:13:08,070 --> 00:13:09,230
Kok cepat banget selesainya?

196
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,250
Bukannya tugasmu masih banyak?

197
00:13:11,350 --> 00:13:12,710
Tapi sekarang semua sudah selesai.

198
00:13:13,610 --> 00:13:15,270
Kamu hebat banget.

199
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:17,870
Kamu orang paling berbakat sedunia.

200
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:20,590
Mau lanjut tidur lagi?

201
00:13:20,770 --> 00:13:23,280
Iya, aku lanjut tidur ya.

202
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,810
Benar?

203
00:13:24,950 --> 00:13:29,150
Iya, aku masih di ranjang, belum bangun.

204
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:32,410
Kalau mau tidur, kenapa lampunya nyala?

205
00:13:32,950 --> 00:13:34,910
Kok kamu tahu?

206
00:13:35,390 --> 00:13:37,240
Coba lihat ke jendela.

207
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:47,270
Pak, paket ekspres Anda sudah sampai.

208
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:50,410
Paket kilat spesial buat pacarku.

209
00:13:52,130 --> 00:13:54,610
Oke, aku turun sekarang.

210
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:58,390
Hati-hati ya.

211
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:13,880
Selamat ulang tahun!

212
00:14:26,810 --> 00:14:28,590
Terima kasih.

213
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:31,230
Makasih banget ya.

214
00:14:43,970 --> 00:14:48,630
Ada yang bilang "nggak apa-apa" kan?

215
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:54,730
Beneran nggak apa-apa, kamu nggak datang juga nggak masalah.

216
00:14:56,790 --> 00:15:00,010
Tapi datang tentu lebih baik.

217
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,930
Lebih baik daripada telpon?

218
00:15:04,310 --> 00:15:06,520
Iya, jauh lebih baik.

219
00:16:25,010 --> 00:16:26,830
Kamu pasti capek banget ya.

220
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:30,560
Udah kerja keras, masih sempat datengin aku.

221
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,610
Sekarang nggak capek sama sekali.

222
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:44,250
Ini apa?

223
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:47,000
Ini...

224
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:49,870
Ehm...

225
00:16:53,970 --> 00:16:58,480
Mungkin tadi nggak sengaja kebawa pas beberes.

226
00:16:59,970 --> 00:17:04,280
Waktu packing, aku nggak bermaksud bawa, sumpah.

227
00:17:05,530 --> 00:17:06,990
Beneran.

228
00:17:13,430 --> 00:17:15,790
Setahuku, tadinya ini di lemari, kan?

229
00:17:16,130 --> 00:17:18,850
Atau aku salah ingat?

230
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:29,630
Iya.

231
00:17:31,470 --> 00:17:33,880
Aku memang mau bawa itu.

232
00:17:35,700 --> 00:17:36,970
Kenapa?

233
00:17:37,810 --> 00:17:40,870
Soalnya aku susah tidur.

234
00:17:49,130 --> 00:17:50,830
Susah tidur?

235
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:58,990
Soalnya nggak biasa tidur sendiri.

236
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:01,960
Biasanya aku peluk kamu kalau tidur.

237
00:18:02,330 --> 00:18:05,220
Tanpa kamu, aku nggak bisa tidur.

238
00:18:08,330 --> 00:18:10,020
Setidaknya...

239
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:13,050
Bajunya masih ada bau kamu.

240
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,060
Duh, jangan dong.

241
00:18:19,870 --> 00:18:22,730
Tolong, jangan godain aku lagi.

242
00:18:26,330 --> 00:18:27,950
Oke deh, aku nggak ngomong lagi.

243
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:32,080
