564
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:35,890
Di sini banyak hiasannya.

565
00:44:36,030 --> 00:44:37,100
Aku beli banyak banget.

566
00:44:50,020 --> 00:44:52,100
Anting baru aku bagus nggak?

567
