Lucu banget!

568
00:44:59,430 --> 00:45:01,390
Kamu jago memuji deh.

569
00:45:08,490 --> 00:45:09,600
Taruh di sini saja.

570
00:45:10,910 --> 00:45:13,510
Menurutmu, letakkan di mana bagusnya?

571
