Tapi nggak ada game baru rilis belakangan ini.

581
00:46:03,230 --> 00:46:05,440
Heh, jangan-jangan emas?

582
00:46:05,700 --> 00:46:08,050
P'Jo, aku suka banget sama emas!

583
00:46:08,670 --> 00:46:09,700
Bukan.

584
00:46:09,900 --> 00:46:12,040
- Eh!
- Aku mau lepasin ya.

585
00:46:23,720 --> 00:46:25,820
Mesin capit anak itu?

586
