Tadi kamu ngomong apa?

632
00:48:55,520 --> 00:48:57,090
Nggak, nggak ada apa-apa.

633
00:48:57,560 --> 00:49:00,100
- Pecahin telur ya? Dipecahin dulu?
- Iya, iya.

634
00:49:01,770 --> 00:49:03,270
P'Jo, pecahin di pinggir mangkok.

635
00:49:04,840 --> 00:49:07,390
Kulit telurnya masuk ke mangkok.

636
00:49:11,040 --> 00:49:13,990
P'Jo, aduknya begini.

637
00:49:14,090 --> 00:49:17,500
Aku contohin, satu-dua-tiga, aduk begini.

638
00:49:18,610 --> 00:49:21,150
Coba lagi.

639
00:49:21,800 --> 00:49:23,300
Aduk sekarang!

640
00:49:23,560 --> 00:49:24,830
Kamu godain lagi, ya?

641
00:49:25,560 --> 00:49:28,880
Tuh kan, dia godain aku lagi.

642
00:49:31,150 --> 00:49:33,030
Nggak kok.

643
00:49:38,890 --> 00:49:41,250
Enak banget, kuemu mantap!

644
00:49:41,260 --> 00:49:42,840
Aku nggak ngapa-ngapain kok.

645
00:49:42,890 --> 00:49:44,630
Aku cuma campurin bahan aja, kok.

646
00:49:44,710 --> 00:49:47,300
Seriusan, enak banget!

647
00:49:48,320 --> 00:49:49,650
Iya.

648
00:49:50,070 --> 00:49:51,400
Cepat banget rasanya.

649
00:49:51,550 --> 00:49:53,510
Kita sudah setahun bareng, loh.

650
00:49:53,510 --> 00:49:54,920
Ayo, kilas balik sebentar.

651
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:55,730
Selama setahun ini...

652
00:49:55,810 --> 00:49:57,060
Kita sudah ngalamin apa aja, ya?

653
